/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時唔好話朋友，親戚都會係咁衰格。"},{"pid":"281dcfc464f7023dabc9c2100fbf0f56dd502ca5","tid":1997510,"uid":201398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:16:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">后</span></span>日"},{"pid":"0313a953d68acf6aeef681dd281863abcc58ad96","tid":1997510,"uid":324041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:16:42.000Z","msg":"香港不嬲都係債仔惡過債主㗎啦！少少錢當買個教訓啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73114af9d01cd108943ce4c221c26a8503a44e5b","tid":1997510,"uid":65201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:17:00.000Z","msg":"私怨擺上來做乜鳩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要連閃卡都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a729ae0daf31c14253fa15884f8ef0f845652552","tid":1997510,"uid":318975,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"281dcfc464f7023dabc9c2100fbf0f56dd502ca5","tid":1997510,"uid":201398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:16:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">后</span></span>日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:17:17.000Z","msg":"佢由2019年已經話會還，仲信佢? 咁財仔唔洗上門啦"},{"pid":"eb3918ba2de4e31ce5d0d4b60a40a3d50ad9ffb4","tid":1997510,"uid":318975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73114af9d01cd108943ce4c221c26a8503a44e5b","tid":1997510,"uid":65201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:17:00.000Z","msg":"私怨擺上來做乜鳩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要連閃卡都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonde