=0b5aea35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ON9Pkva.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FON9Pkva.jpg&h=42395e88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我都係學生，啲錢草咗好耐，以為會還&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"1889d2022dbead27129b3b0666c617849b160af1","tid":1997510,"uid":62749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:23:32.000Z","msg":"雖然對你黎講好似好大數目<br />\n但呢筆咁既數幫你趕走左個潛在炸彈, 都未嘗唔係好事<br />\n如果等你出黎做野佢先借, 可能後面加多個零"},{"pid":"82a3ed57498abdb3b787ac82d0e9d160b6c20bfe","tid":1997510,"uid":127044,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:29:53.000Z","msg":"點解要還 人地自己本事借番黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a6dabd13426473e8270373be2a79145665ce471","tid":1997510,"uid":88982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:32:49.000Z","msg":"樓豬雖然你係ON9仔<br />\n但係我都要講一句<br />\n下次唔好再借錢比人喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25aba34f4de6dd2963611e8336cc9a6940bb22b2","tid":1997510,"uid":318975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1889d2022dbead27129b3b0666c617849b160af1","tid":1997510,"uid":62749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:23:32.000Z","msg":"雖然對你黎講好似好大數目<br />\n但呢筆咁既數幫你趕走左個潛在炸彈, 都未嘗唔係好事<br />\n如果等你出黎做野佢先借, 可能後面加多個零"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:33:21.000Z","msg":"咁樣諗的確會好過啲，多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ecc18e743200afab9b2c45552c47075ad4bddeb","tid":1997510,"uid":2267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T17:34:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4pTwyUo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4pTwyUo.jpg&h=8e063d8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7d6358f44653eac1d6883ff8bcdf66ebf789b3c","tid":1997510,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc1215dc51a488fc9a8a588a81e8891e4a1d6afb","tid":1997510,"uid":318975,"li